extendedInfo.description: Expense Tracker is an application for managing your expenses and incomes. With Expense Tracker you can easily track your daily expenses and income with best reporting and charts options .This application provides you the following best features:Features. Tracking expenses and incomes by week, month and year as well as by categories. Simple and Best UI that enable you to use the application any where at any time.. Quick scroll and select option for Selecting categories and title you already entered.This makes very simple to enter an expense or income with out typing much.. Best Log Report with multiple filter options like expense and income  separately or combined and By dates as This Year,This Month,Today and with more like Select a Year,Month,Date. . Best Chart Reports with Pie Chart and Bar Chart Model. . Export / Import options for taking Backup Database and also Import Existing Database.. Also provides SkyDrive Cloud storage support for Export / Import Database directly and quickly from application.. Export to CSV Options for Reports with multiple filters based on type( Expense/Income/Combined ) and date filters.. Export and share options are added for more easier management of reports and data.. CSV Export can be done as combined with selected categories..Export to PDF  is also added newly for better exporting option of your reports..Print Option is also added to app for print the reports directly form mobile .Google Cloud Print is the another major feature.It enable you to export and print you reports on the go to you home printer or office printer remotely.System Requirements. Android 2.2 and abovePlease send your valuable comments and suggestions to our email id : beliketapt@gmail.com. Your suggestions will make this app more useful.Keywords: expense manager, expense management, expense tracker, money manager, personal money manager, savings tracker, saving money, finance, finance manager, personal finance, personal finance manager, personal finance management, personal money management, budget manager, budget tracker, spending tracker, daily expense tracker, daily expense manager, income track,expense log,financial planner, smart financial calculator, accounting, finance, accounting software, business accounting, cash register, cash organizer, money, money saving app, money saver, easy money, pocket money, ledger, page once, mint, checkbook, book keeping, book keeper, mobile expense tracker, mobile money app, mobile money manager, daily expense tracking, daily money managementPlease feel free to suggest your interests and suggestions to us/what else do you want inside this application to make your needs complete. We are considering them as high value so that we can satisfy our users completely.
